00:41:07,068 --> 00:41:09,503
-I didn't say yes to you.

878
00:41:09,537 --> 00:41:10,537
-Well.

879
00:41:21,916 --> 00:41:24,618
[boat blaring]

880
00:41:24,652 --> 00:41:27,722
[birds squawking]

881
00:41:35,129 --> 00:41:38,299
