883
00:41:41,602 --> 00:41:43,838
Okay?

884
00:41:43,871 --> 00:41:46,607
He and my old man,
they go way back.

885
00:41:46,640 --> 00:41:48,542
They'll figure it out.

886
00:41:48,576 --> 00:41:51,979
