894
00:42:14,268 --> 00:42:16,771
for Mister McLaughlin,

895
00:42:16,804 --> 00:42:19,774
which I guess that is kind of
true, but what nobody knows

896
00:42:19,807 --> 00:42:22,176
is that the coon my
old man killed, he...

897
00:42:22,209 --> 00:42:23,320
