tell me this, John.

898
00:42:23,344 --> 00:42:25,846
I, um... it's all right.

899
00:42:25,880 --> 00:42:27,948
-Just listen to me.
I'm gonna tell you.

900
00:42:27,982 --> 00:42:31,919
Um, the coon my old man killed,
